# Pin lint behavior to the rule set this codebase was formatted under.
# Newer swiftformat releases enable new rules by default; disable those
# rather than churning the whole repo (pippin-eai session, 2026-07-13).
--disable wrapIfStatementBodies,docComments,noForceUnwrapInTests,wrapPropertyBodies,wrapMultilineStatementBraces,blankLinesAroundMark
